text: Jack Oliver Ian Campbell (born 11 November 1999) is an English cricketer. In July 2018, he played for the England under-19 cricket team against South Africa. He made his first-class debut on 26 March 2019, for Durham MCCU against Durham, as part of the Marylebone Cricket Club University fixtures. ==References== ==External links== * Category:1999 births Category:Living people Category:English cricketers Category:Durham MCCU cricketers Category:Durham cricketers Category:Sportspeople from Portsmouth
